{"content": "I need to solve 893 \u00d7 546 in base 11.\n\nFirst, let me convert these base 11 numbers to base 10:\n- 893\u2081\u2081 = 8\u00d711\u00b2 + 9\u00d711\u00b9 + 3\u00d711\u2070 = 8\u00d7121 + 9\u00d711 + 3 = 968 + 99 + 3 = 1070\u2081\u2080\n- 546\u2081\u2081 = 5\u00d711\u00b2 + 4\u00d711\u00b9 + 6\u00d711\u2070 = 5\u00d7121 + 4\u00d711 + 6 = 605 + 44 + 6 = 655\u2081\u2080\n\nNow multiply in base 10:\n1070 \u00d7 655 = 700,850\u2081\u2080\n\nNow convert 700,850\u2081\u2080 back to base 11:\n700,850 \u00f7 11 = 63,713 remainder 7\n63,713 \u00f7 11 = 5,792 remainder 1\n5,792 \u00f7 11 = 526 remainder 6\n526 \u00f7 11 = 47 remainder 9\n47 \u00f7 11 = 4 remainder 3\n4 \u00f7 11 = 0 remainder 4\n\nReading the remainders from bottom to top: 439617\u2081\u2081\n\nLet me verify: 4\u00d711\u2075 + 3\u00d711\u2074 + 9\u00d711\u00b3 + 6\u00d711\u00b2 + 1\u00d711\u00b9 + 7\u00d711\u2070\n= 4\u00d7161,051 + 3\u00d714,641 + 9\u00d71,331 + 6\u00d7121 + 1\u00d711 + 7\n= 644,204 + 43,923 + 11,979 + 726 + 11 + 7\n= 700,850 \u2713\n\n439617", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 182, "completion_tokens": 477}